<br>
The whole thing is unchallenging, anti social, cookie cutter bullshit. It is a mind numbingly boring timesink of points farming and nothing else. All you people who keep saying how &quot;fun&quot; it is can kiss my ass. Am I the only person who is completely jaded by the whole thing already?<br>
<br>
One thing is finally crystal clear to me, the Everquest I fell in love with a few years ago is gone forever, and no one at Sony will be bringing it back. I saw this coming but like any good addiciton/love affair I kept coming back for more. I have no problem with time sinks for advancement per se, but this is just too boring for words. The zones are uninspiring and bland, they are not dungeons in the traditional EQ sense and selling this garbage as a dungeon crawl expansion is utter horseshit. LDoN is, in short, the most stupidly repetitive thing ever in EQ and that is really saying something.<br>
<br>
