<br>
One group I was in we had a ranger who ranger gated 4 times and de-leveled. When we popped all his corpses where there and we called a cleric friend to rez those of us that needed it. We offered donations which she refused but we convinced her to take some Dots so all was good.<br>
<br>
Not the best solution but an option. Persoanlly I'm against rezzing in the dungeon especially when doing the hard levels. In a group last night, wiped when a trap went off and poisoned whole group. We lost 15 minutes while people ran for fresh KEI, cause my C2 isn't good enough apparently, and some demanded rezzes. Complete waste of time IMHO.<br>
<br>
96 rez at end of crawl should be the same as 96 rez in middle of crawl. We fell short of our goal and that 15 minutes would have made the difference.<br>
